<h1 style="background-color:SlateBlue;">How to make a toast </h1>
<ul>
<li>Step 1: Choose your bread (white, whole wheat, or any other type you prefer).</li>
<li>Step 2: Place the bread in a toaster or on a grill.</li> <li>Step 3: Set the toaster to your desired level of browning.</li>
<li>Step 4: Start the toaster and wait until the toast pops up or the bread is golden and crispy.</li>
<li>Step 5: Carefully remove the toast from the toaster using tongs or your fingers (it may be hot).</li>
<li>Step 6: Optional â€“ Add toppings such as butter, jam, or other spreads.</li>
<li>Step 7: Serve and enjoy your toast!</li>
